(Deep Contemplation)

00:22:17.849 --> 00:22:19.040
(Mastery of Heaven and Earth)

00:22:19.040 --> 00:22:26.129
ظآزIf you treat pain as swallowed needlesظآز

00:22:27.601 --> 00:22:38.008
ظآزThe scars etched sharpen the heart to a bladeظآز

