ظآزTowards mountains, chase the stars brightظآز

00:43:58.096 --> 00:44:03.792
ظآزBoth joy and grief make the trip worthwhileظآز

00:44:04.304 --> 00:44:12.912
ظآزTrying to catch up to your own lost shadowظآز

00:44:13.808 --> 00:44:19.312
ظآزWithin the wilds, echoes thriveظآز

00:44:19.312 --> 00:44:24.816
ظآزClear mind leads to a clear pathظآز

00:44:24.880 --> 00:44:28.944
ظآزBe grateful to your lossesظآز

00:44:29.232 --> 00:44:34.456
ظآزMake your steps weightlessظآز

00:44:35.056 --> 00:44:38.768
ظآزTowards mountains, chase the stars brightظآز

