ظآزLet time embrace you and wash away the pastظآز

00:44:45.232 --> 00:44:53.200
ظآزPut every twist behind you, drift leisurely through timeظآز

00:44:54.608 --> 00:44:59.856
ظآزMake headway against the wind, let mountains bow to your paceظآز

00:45:00.112 --> 00:45:06.016
ظآزRush towards a life without regretظآز

00:45:06.016 --> 00:45:10.136
ظآزLet your nature burst freeظآز

00:45:10.352 --> 00:45:15.088
ظآزUnbound by formظآز

